arance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step3"><label>Bring it down across the front of abdomen to right groin , crossing the first turn of bandage there</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step4"><label>Then pass the bandage across the front of right thigh, to outer side , round the back to inner side of left thigh to complete turn . make series of these turns , bearing in mind that the bandage must be passed round the waist up to level of naval</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1></group></h:body></h:html>